name: Kimjor #5 I'm Cupidd, Momm.
description:
Welcome to the world of Kim Jor. A mischievous little Forpus who loves to travel around in his mother's dreamland. This is the first NFT in KimJor Roadmap. You will get beautiful images in a variety of styles with the purple forpus is hidden. 

Today Kim Jor wants to be a six-winged little cupid. He and his lovely friends float on the chocolate clouds. Let's love each other. Happy Valentine's Day and enjoy your dream world.
